claim.claim-text:
9. A vision enhancement system for a vehicle, the vehicle having an interior, comprising: 
a camera configured to view a rear seat area of the vehicle interior and to generate a video signal representative of the rear seat area of the vehicle interior; 
a display coupled to the camera, wherein the display is configured to display the video signal; 
a light source positioned proximate the rear seat area of the vehicle interior configured to illuminate the rear seat area; and 
an operator input device, wherein the display is configured to display the video signal in response to operator actuation of the operator input device and wherein the light source is automatically turned on when the video signal is displayed using the operator input device.
